# Correct Supervisor Role Permissions

This plan corrects an oversight where the **Supervisor** role was functionally restricted to the same level as a standard **Officer** for sensitive operations. We will elevate the Supervisor's permissions to allow them to manage operational security (Watchlist) and access their own account settings.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Supervisors** will gain full Add/Delete authority for the National Watchlist.
> **Supervisors** will now be able to access the "Settings" page to manage their own passcodes.
> **Personnel Management** will remain strictly restricted to **Administrators**.

